parameters: It's a statue of a naked woman.
It somehow resembles a shrine maiden..
(..It feels like I'm being glared at.. Maybe it's just my imagination..)

(..It's creepy.. Even when I look away.. Those eyes, they're burned into my
mind..)
It's a statue of a naked woman.
"I feel like I've seen this somewhere before.."
"..Please, please, let them be born safely.."
(Maybe it's the god of safe childbirth..?)

"Thanks to this, our village has become fruitful and we all carry its child
within us.."

(..This seems like a really suspicious religion.. No, it's definitely a
messed up religion..)
"Is this an examination? Or is it childbirth?"
"..Yes, I have had sex with him many times-"
"That's great.. I've only done it twice myself.."
"Since you got pregnant from that, you must have a wonderful womb."

"(We've been talking about nothing but lewd stuff.. ugh.. it's hard to
walk..)"
"Oh.. what a lovely guest we have here."

(My, that belly is so big.. I wonder if it's going to give birth soon..
Even though it looks a little older than me..)

"It's alright.. Yes, if there's anything that's bothering you, please don't
hesitate to ask."
"..Um, well then.. W-What does it feel like to.. um, be pregnant?"
"Um, well.. it's because it's so different from the outside world.."

"Well.. I don't know much about the outside world either, but if it's my
personal opinion.."

"It's wonderful to be able to fully feel the fact that I have been
impregnated.."

"As the fetus grows slowly.. every time I feel its movements, I feel the
greatness of my master who violated me. The fact that I was violated and
impregnated is always there."

"And.. the fact that I will give birth. The sense of accomplishment of
fulfilling my duty as a female to give birth to the master's child.. the
pride of offering the greatest approval as a female to the master.. all of
it is felt as love."
"..Fufu, it's not something that's easy to tell to a man.."

"Anyway, for a female, being impregnated is an honor in itself.. and the
sense of accomplishment when giving birth is indescribable."
(Oh! I can't.. I'm a boy right now--)

Hinori's small uterus throbbed, whether it was protesting against the
deceit or agreeing with it. It made her uneasy, as if the madness of the
villagers had infected her.
"Oh.. I'm sorry. We were told we could come and observe.."

"Oh.. it's not a visit to offer condolences. It's rare to have visitors for
observation.."

(W-Wow.. the belly really sticks out like that. It's different from just
being fat.)

"Having only men would be boring. Hehe, I'm sorry, but since most of the
people here are under the master's command.. it might be difficult to find
a partner for you."
"I-It's not like I had that intention.."

"Hehe, however, since this is a facility that you will eventually rely on..
and since all villagers born here will inevitably rely on this facility, I
think it's a very good thing to observe."
"..Yes, I have had sex with him many times-"
"That's great.. I've only done it twice myself.."
"Since you got pregnant from that, you must have a wonderful womb."

"(Somehow.. we're only talking about erotic things.. ugh.. it's hard to
walk.)"
